properties.Name: ChannelProgram
properties.Description: The Program(s) that support or are applicable to a Channel.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: MarketingProgramId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Program.

Columns.Name: StartDate
Columns.Description: The date upon which the Channel began participation in the Program.

Columns.Name: EndDate
Columns.Description: The date upon which the Channel terminated or ceased to participate in the Program.

Columns.Name: PromotionalAllowanceAmount
Columns.Description: An incentive amount given to a Channel for participating in a Program.

Columns.Name: CoopAdvertisingIndicator
Columns.Description: A flag or indicator denoting that the Channel has a cooperative advertising relationship.

Columns.Name: Note
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information related to the Channel Program relationship.
